              sidebar:
                "[![](https://fediseer.com/api/v1/badges/guarantees/lemmy.dbzer0.com.svg)\n![](https://fediseer.com/api/v1/badges/endorsements/lemmy.dbzer0.com.svg)](https://gui.fediseer.com/instances/detail/lemmy.dbzer0.com) \n\nCommunities about Anarchism, Generative AI, Copylefts, Neurodivergence, Filesharing, and Free Software. (And Math!)\n\nFollow the [Anarchist Code of Conduct](https://wiki.dbzer0.com/divisions-by-zero/the-anarchist-code-of-conduct/) and honor the [Disengage Rule](https://wiki.dbzer0.com/divisions-by-zero/the-disengage-rule/).\n\nDon't be shitty to each other. Keep it SFW. Obey the spirit of [The Golden Rules](https://wiki.dbzer0.com/divisions-by-zero/the-golden-rules/). Fuck around and find out.  \n\n---\n\nüë∂ New to lemmy? [Start here](https://lemmy.dbzer0.com/post/23808) and [here](https://lemmy.dbzer0.com/c/newtolemmy@lemmy.ca)\n\n---\n\nPlease help cover server costs\n\n| [![Ko-Fi](https://lemmy.dbzer0.com/pictrs/image/4a2f073a-3dd8-492a-942d-72bd929c9f1d.png)](https://ko-fi.com/dbzer0) | [![Liberapay](https://lemmy.dbzer0.com/pictrs/image/eec4659d-39be-4fc9-bc9e-66a96285ea2c.png)](https://liberapay.com/db0/) |\n|:--:|:--:| \n| [*Ko-fi*](https://ko-fi.com/dbzer0) | [*Liberapay*](https://liberapay.com/db0/)  |\n\n---\n\n\nThis instance provides [a wiki service](https://wiki.dbzer0.com/) which only users of this lemmy can use. If you want a wiki for your community or your account or whatever, feel free to use it\n\n---\n\nThis instance currently allows new community creation, however the following subjects are explicitly not allowed as communities. \n\n* Nothing positive or promoting cryptocurrency, blockchain or NFTs\n* Nothing extreme-right-wing. This includes conspiracy theories, SovCit, Pro-Police, AnCaps etc. We'll know it when we see it, don't test us!\n* No anti-science topics.\n* No Tankie shit.\n* No TERFs.\n* No Porn.\n\nPreferably you'll stay within the topics endorsed by this instance (see first line)\n\nNote that you are expected to attempt to create an active community and not just squat on a name. [Inactive communities will be purged](https://lemmy.dbzer0.com/post/56147) after receiving a warning.\n\n---\n\nJoin the [/0 Chat Rooms](https://matrix.to/!divisions-by-zero:matrix.org#/#divisions-by-zero:matrix.org) and Matrix and regale us with your tales of adventure!\n\n**NEW** Now you can also join the [Fediverse Anarchist Flotilla Matrix Space](https://matrix.to/#/#fediverse-anarchist-flotilla:anarchist.nexus) where most of our general inter-instance chat rooms are now located!\n\n---\n\nWhen going to other communities, respect their rules AND our rules when they are more restrictive. Do not give cause for others to de-federate our instance please.\n\n---\n\nAlternative Frontends\n\n* [voyager](https://v.lemmy.dbzer0.com/)\n* [photon](https://p.lemmy.dbzer0.com/)\n* [alexandrite](https://a.lemmy.dbzer0.com/)\n* [tesseract](https://t.lemmy.dbzer0.com/)",
