              published: "2023-07-09T01:44:29.950799Z",
              sidebar:
                "### What is Lemmy?\nLeminal Space is an instance of the social link aggregation and discussion platform [Lemmy](https://join-lemmy.org/). It is completely free and open, and not controlled by any company. This means that there is no advertising, tracking, or secret algorithms. Content is organised into communities, so it is easy to subscribe to topics that you are interested in, and ignore others. Voting is used to bring the most interesting items to the top.\n\n*If you can't find the community you'd like to join in the [All Communities](https://leminal.space/communities?listingType=All&amp%3Bpage=0) section, try searching for it on the Lemmy Explorer [communities page](https://lemmyverse.net/communities), then copy and paste the community link in the [Search](https://leminal.space/search?type=Communities&amp%3BlistingType=All&amp%3Bpage=1&amp%3Bsort=TopAll) box.*\n\n**Featured Communities:**\n- [!technology@lemmy.world](https://leminal.space/c/technology@lemmy.world)\n- [!games@sh.itjust.works](https://leminal.space/c/games@sh.itjust.works)\n- [!asklemmy@lemmy.ml](https://leminal.space/c/asklemmy@lemmy.ml)\n- [!aww@lemmy.world](https://leminal.space/c/aww@lemmy.world)\n- [!worldnews@lemmy.ml](https://leminal.space/c/worldnews@lemmy.ml)\n- [!cat@lemmy.world](https://leminal.space/c/cat@lemmy.world)\n\n**Meta Communities:**\n- [Leminal Space](https://leminal.space/c/leminalspace) (announcements)\n- [Leminal Space Meta](https://leminal.space/c/leminalspacemeta) (discussion)\n\n---\n### Code of Conduct\n1. Bigotry will not be tolerated. This includes racism, sexism, ableism, homophobia or transphobia. Please also familiarise yourself with the Lemmy [Code of Conduct](https://join-lemmy.org/docs/code_of_conduct.html).\n2. While this is tacitly covered by rule #1, for the sake of clarity: fascist or alt-right discourse is not welcome here.\n3. Be respectful.\n4. No pornography.\n5. No advertising or spam.\n\n---\n#### Donations\nIf you would like to contribute towards our running costs, you can donate through the below platforms.\n\n[![Liberapay](https://leminal.space/pictrs/image/d69814de-eeb2-484f-becc-9b886e0a663b.png) Liberapay](https://liberapay.com/leminal.space/)\n[![Ko-fi](https://leminal.space/pictrs/image/ea0aafdb-203e-46b4-8dcf-355bc5b83f3b.png) Ko-fi](https://ko-fi.com/leminalspace)\n[![Patreon](https://leminal.space/pictrs/image/499b554b-b251-4b3c-a84c-e2d188c0a7ec.png) Patreon](https://www.patreon.com/leminalspace)\n\n---\n#### Status & Frontends\n[![Uptime](https://leminal.space/status/api/badge/10/uptime?color=ff56c2&style=flat-square&label=24h)](https://status.leminal.space/) [![Alexandrite front-end status](https://leminal.space/status/api/badge/12/status?upColor=ff56c2&style=flat-square&downLabel=Dn&label=Alexandrite)](https://alex.leminal.space/)\n\n[![Photon front-end status](https://leminal.space/status/api/badge/35/status?upColor=ff56c2&style=flat-square&downLabel=Dn&label=Photon)](https://photon.leminal.space/) [![Tesseract front-end status](https://leminal.space/status/api/badge/33/status?upColor=ff56c2&style=flat-square&downLabel=Dn&label=Tesseract)](https://tes.leminal.space/)\n\n[Status Page](https://status.leminal.space/)\n\n#",
